org.eclipse.modisco.jee.ejbjar.EjbJar11
Interface SessionType

public interface SessionType

A representation of the model object 'Session Type'.

The following features are supported:

  • Description
  • Display Name
  • Small Icon
  • Large Icon
  • Ejb Name
  • Home
  • Remote
  • Ejb Class
  • Session Type
  • Transaction Type
  • Env Entry
  • Ejb Ref
  • Security Role Ref
  • Resource Ref
  • Id
